Package: sphericalDepth
Type: Package
Title: Computation of the spherical halfspace depth
Version: 0.9.0
Author: Rainer Dyckerhoff
Maintainer: Rainer Dyckerhoff <rainer.dyckerhoff@statistik.uni-koeln.de>
Description: This package provides two routines to compute the spherical halfspace depth, also known as angular halfspace depth or angular Tukey depth. For a description of the algorithms, see: Dyckerhoff, R., Nagy, S. (2024) Exact computation of angular halfspace depth.
